syntax.ban:
The time limit to be specified is 7 days.
If the specified time exceeds 7 days, it will be reset to 7 days.
The messages will be deleted according to the specified time.
Putting a reason is not mandatory.
syntax.channelMember:
The available arguments are:
- **join** will define the channel where the welcome announcements will appear.
- **leave** will define the channel where the departure announcements will appear.

After these arguments, the available arguments are **channel ID/mention**, **reset** and **this** :
- **channel ID/mention** will define the channel by its ID or mention.
- **reset** will reset the channel that has been configured.
- **this** will define the channel where the order was made.
syntax.createChannel:
The only two arguments to specify for the type are "**text**" and "**voice**"..
- The argument "**text**" will define a textual channel.
- The argument "**voice**" will define a voice room.
The name of the new salon must not exceed 100 characters.
You can choose to specify a category for the salon to be classified in or not.
syntax.invite:
The only two arguments available are **create** and **bot**.
The **create** argument will create a new server invitation link.
The **bot** argument will send the bot invitation link.
syntax.joinRole:
The available arguments are:
- **channel ID/mention** will define the role thanks to its ID or its mention.
- **reset** will reset the role that has been configured.
syntax.localization:
The available languages are:
:flag_us: / :flag_gb: en
:flag_fr: fr
If the language is not configured, it will default to English.
syntax.mute: Putting a reason is not mandatory.
syntax.prohibit:
The available arguments are **add**, **rem** and **reset**.
- **add** will add a word to the list of forbidden words.
- **rem** will remove a word from the list of prohibited words.
- **reset** will reset the entire list of forbidden words.
After the arguments **add** and **rem**, you must put the argument **word** which will correspond to the word that will be added or removed.
syntax.purge: The number of messages to specify must be between **0** and **101**.
syntax.say: When you don't have permission to manage messages, the bot will include your name. Conversely, it will not.
